By end-user, the hospital's segment accounted for the highest revenue-grossing segment in the global NUT midline carcinoma treatment market in 2023. The specialty clinics segment is predicted to grow at the fastest CAGR during the forecast period owing to the rise in outpatient care and focus on targeted therapies in specialized settings.

